1.1.name: wordpress/wp-ultimate-menu-maker-lite
1.1.description: Wordpress Ultimate Restaurant Menu Maker allows you to create any number of menues to use on your restaurant / cafe web sites. Easy drang and srop system allows you to edit menues on fly. Categories, multiprice system, standart Wordpress interface allows you to create and modify your menues in a simple way.
